txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Sticky filth from the insects west of the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul at the outpost on the shores of Lake Evendim.
'There is something to be found in everything that might appear useless. Some of the filth left by insects has a use, and we would like it here.'
Wardens of Ann√∫minas Task: Sticky Filth
Tinnudir, a Ranger-outpost on the eastern shore of Lake Evendim, is home to the Rangers of Evendim. There, at the outpost, a Ranger named Astiul awaits the return of sticky filth.
Deliver the sticky filth to Astiul at the Ranger-outpost of Tinnudir
You have been tasked with collecting sticky filth from the insects west of Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul within the lakeside outpost.
Wanted: Sticky filth from the insects west of the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir.
